== Deaths == * Year 1 of {{ill|Shuchō|ja|朱鳥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 1|ja|10月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[686]] ) – {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 40th emperor of Japan. * Year 5 of {{ill|Jitō|ja|Empress Jitō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 6|ja|10月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[691]] ) – {{ill|Prince Kawashima|ja|川島皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , Japanese imperial prince (b. [[657]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Eishō|ja|永正|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1504]] ) – {{ill|Mogami Yoshizumi|ja|最上義淳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * Year 14 of {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , [[1586]] ) – {{ill|Takikawa Kazumasu|ja|滝川一益|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , samurai commander (b. [[1525]] ).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Chōyō Festival|ja|重陽|1=Double Ninth Festival|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} Festival. ** *Kiku-no-sake* (菊御酒, *Chikūjakī*) – In {{ill|Okinawa Prefecture|ja|沖縄県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , sake with floating chrysanthemum petals is offered to household altars and fire gods to pray for family safety. * Senior Citizens' Day ({{CHN|qq=}} , {{lang-zh|老年节|qq=}} ) – Defined in Article 9 of the {{ill|PRC Elderly Rights Protection Law|ja|中華人民共和国老年人権益保障法|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .<ref name="jil">{{Cite web|和書|url=http://www.jil.go.jp/foreign/jihou/2013_7/china_05.html|title=「高齢者権益保障法」が7月に施行―「喜憂半々」の受け止め、期待と不安と|date=2013-07|publisher={{ill|Japan Institute for Labour Policy and Training|ja|労働政策研究・研修機構|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} |accessdate=2016-01-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117131729/http://www.jil.go.jp/foreign/jihou/2013_7/china_05.html|archivedate=2016-01-17|qq=}} </ref> * {{ill|Kugatsukunchi|ja|クガツクンチ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , celebrated in the {{ill|Amami Islands|ja|奄美群島|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
