{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:17, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月初九|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 9일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 9''' is the 9th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} . == Events == * Year 4 of {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 22|qq=}} , [[1871]] ) – The "Noon Cannon System" ({{ill|午砲の制|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/午砲の制|qq=}} ) was enacted, establishing the practice of firing a cannon at noon from the former main keep of {{ill|Edo Castle|ja|江戸城|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Castle|qq=}} to signal the time.
== Births == * Year 13 of {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōreki|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 15|qq=}} , [[1763]] ) – {{ill|Tani Bunchō|ja|谷文晁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tani Bunchō|qq=}} , {{ill|painter|ja|Painter|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/painter|qq=}} (d. [[1841]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Kyōwa|ja|享和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōwa|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 16|qq=}} , [[1801]] ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saijun|ja|徳川斉順|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Saijun|qq=}} , 11th {{ill|Daimyō|ja|大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daimyō|qq=}} of {{ill|Kishū Domain|ja|紀州藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kishū Domain|qq=}} (d. [[1846]] ). * Year 11 of {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 17|qq=}} , [[1828]] ) – {{ill|Soejima Taneomi|ja|副島種臣|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soejima Taneomi|qq=}} , {{ill|Minister of Foreign Affairs (Japan)|ja|外務卿|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minister of Foreign Affairs (Japan)|qq=}} and Minister of Home Affairs (d. [[1905]] ). * Year 3 of {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 6|ja|10月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 6|qq=}} , [[1867]] ) – {{ill|Hirayama Shin|ja|平山信|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirayama Shin|qq=}} , {{ill|astronomer|ja|天文学者|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/astronomer|qq=}} (d. [[1945]] ).
== Deaths == * Year 1 of {{ill|Shuchō|ja|朱鳥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shuchō|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 1|ja|10月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 1|qq=}} , [[686]] ) – {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|Emperor Tenmu|1=Emperor Tenmu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Tenmu|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Tenmu|qq=}} , 40th emperor of Japan. * Year 5 of {{ill|Jitō|ja|Empress Jitō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jitō|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 6|ja|10月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 6|qq=}} , [[691]] ) – {{ill|Prince Kawashima|ja|川島皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Kawashima|qq=}} , Japanese imperial prince (b. [[657]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Eishō|ja|永正|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eishō|qq=}} (Julian calendar {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 16|qq=}} , [[1504]] ) – {{ill|Mogami Yoshizumi|ja|最上義淳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mogami Yoshizumi|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyō|ja|戦国大名|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyō|qq=}} . * Year 14 of {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} , [[1586]] ) – {{ill|Takikawa Kazumasu|ja|滝川一益|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takikawa Kazumasu|qq=}} , samurai commander (b. [[1525]] ).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Chōyō Festival|ja|重陽|1=Double Ninth Festival|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōyō Festival|13=User:Immanuelle/Double Ninth Festival|qq=}} Festival. ** *Kiku-no-sake* (菊御酒, *Chikūjakī*) – In {{ill|Okinawa Prefecture|ja|沖縄県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okinawa Prefecture|qq=}} , sake with floating chrysanthemum petals is offered to household altars and fire gods to pray for family safety. * Senior Citizens' Day ({{CHN|qq=}} , {{lang-zh|老年节|qq=}} ) – Defined in Article 9 of the {{ill|PRC Elderly Rights Protection Law|ja|中華人民共和国老年人権益保障法|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/PRC Elderly Rights Protection Law|qq=}} .<ref name="jil">{{Cite web|和書|url=http://www.jil.go.jp/foreign/jihou/2013_7/china_05.html|title=「高齢者権益保障法」が7月に施行―「喜憂半々」の受け止め、期待と不安と|date=2013-07|publisher={{ill|Japan Institute for Labour Policy and Training|ja|労働政策研究・研修機構|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japan Institute for Labour Policy and Training|qq=}} |accessdate=2016-01-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117131729/http://www.jil.go.jp/foreign/jihou/2013_7/china_05.html|archivedate=2016-01-17|qq=}} </ref> * {{ill|Kugatsukunchi|ja|クガツクンチ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kugatsukunchi|qq=}} , celebrated in the {{ill|Amami Islands|ja|奄美群島|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Amami Islands|qq=}} .
